Class Int4

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.math.vector.Int4
All Implemented Interfaces:
IntVector<Int4,Float4>, Vector<Integer,Int4>, Group<Integer>, Serializable
public class Int4 extends Object implements IntVector<Int4,Float4>
A four-dimensional vector which uses the type int.
